  "texts": [
    "The knowledge distillation process further enabled a smaller student model to approximate the performance of the original LLama 2, demonstrating the viability of these techniques in producing more efficient LLMs.",
    "The findings from this research have significant implications for the development of efficient LLMs.",
    "By demonstrating that it is possible to substantially reduce the resource requirements of such models while maintaining high levels of performance, we contribute to the ongoing efforts to make LLMs more accessible and sustainable.",
    "This is particularly relevant in contexts where computational resources are limited, such as edge computing and mobile applications, broadening the potential applications of LLMs.",
    "Our research contributes valuable insights into the potential for model compression and knowledge distillation to produce more efficient and accessible LLMs."
